{"tid":790886,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工作態度不佳　日男被老闆帶到山上綑綁毒打","createTime":"2018-08-23T11:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T11:15:32.000Z","uid":122,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9853538518028a08d80c38f6823ec9d7781a1aea","tid":790886,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"日本長崎縣松浦市一名19歲的男子，因為工作態度不佳，惹火老闆和學長，而被2人帶到山上毒打。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，29歲的建設公司代表前田龍二，與在該公司任職的21歲員工布施涼太，在上周六（18日）晚上7點多，開車把同公司一名19歲的員工載到松浦市今福町的山中後，用預先準備好的繩子，把他綁在樹上，再用地上的斷木痛毆他，把人打到骨折。<br />\n<br />\n兩人被警方逮捕後坦承施暴。警方研判，兩人是因為不滿被害人平日的工作態度，才憤而犯案。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"6cb8152bae182269346d814d8fe37658c05c7cd8","tid":790886,"uid":155818,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:03:21.000Z","msg":"痴撚線公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95db77fe8f0f3b59e8bef6baed4f2a8132d157c9","tid":790886,"uid":3454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:03:31.000Z","msg":"往死裡打"},{"pid":"7ae1f42b510d3c6712d11e53e0e70dd7e3a54433","tid":790886,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:03:35.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"4b56f641797650aed0a3013e12aae851dcb08385","tid":790886,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"返去先下手為強 捉左老闆同上司先"},{"pid":"fc6469d8e8ac1bee2d161e2a790a34e5e430528c","tid":790886,"uid":123264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:04:01.000Z","msg":"前田龍二<br />\n個名好形象化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2be029c1fa26218df9f065f8c108f7412cbed5e","tid":790886,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:04:07.000Z","msg":"垃圾00後<br />\n死日本仔同支那人一齊玩抖音玩壞腦"},{"pid":"632dda1c6c863a3b569a48d3e75ce6f9cb151292","tid":790886,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c